These are the tags for various copyrights:

\textsuperscript{\textregistered}
\textsuperscript{\textcopyright}
\texttrademark


Also you can define a shortcut:

% Registered definieren
\def\SymbReg{\textsuperscript{\textregistered}}
 
\begin{document}
   % Registered-Zeichen erstellen
   \SymbReg
\end{document}

Source: http://blog.mixable.de/latex-trademark-copyright-registered/
